### Create Product Type
# POST http://localhost:9000/api/product-types
# Content-Type: application/json

# {
#   "name": "T-Shirts",
#   "description": "All types of t-shirts for men",
#   "image": {
#     "url": "https://example.com/images/tshirt.jpg",
#     "publicId": "product-types/tshirt",
#     "alt": "T-Shirt"
#   },
#   "order": 1
# }

### Get All Product Types
GET http://localhost:9000/api/products
# GET http://localhost:9000/api/products/limited-edition-long-wool-trench-coat-020820

### Get Single Product Type
# GET http://localhost:9000/api/product-types/{{PRODUCT_TYPE_ID}}

### Update Product Type
# PUT http://localhost:9000/api/product-types/{{PRODUCT_TYPE_ID}}
# Content-Type: application/json

# {
#   "name": "Updated T-Shirts",
#   "description": "Updated description for t-shirts",
#   "order": 2
# }

# ### Delete Product Type
# DELETE http://localhost:9000/api/product-types/{{PRODUCT_TYPE_ID}}

### Update Product - Fix productType (when productType is null or deleted)
